Package: pivotdata
Type: Package
Title: Convert Wide Format to Long Format
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Xinyi", "Zhao",
      email = "xz@example.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides functions to convert datasets from wide format to long format.
    Includes support for renaming value columns dynamically and handling 
    year columns from 2000 to 2019 for datasets such as mortality or other indicators.
